                  references or direct sources to build the dictionary. Depending on the cases, this
                  step may require digitizing printed text (see the
                  related scenario on <ref type="link"
                     target="http://ssk.huma-num.fr/#/scenarios/SSK_sc_digitization"
                     >digitization</ref>), and/or build a normalized and lemmatized corpus (see <ref
                        type="link"
                        target="http://ssk.huma-num.fr/#/scenarios/SSK_sc_corpusModellingInTEI/8"
                        >here</ref> the related scenario).</desc>
